    tmp = (tmp / wp.exp((v2 + 0.70 - v2 + 0.58)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v2 + 0.99) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.56)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.97)) / ((v0 + 0.66 / tmp + 0.84) * (v1 + 0.99 - v0 + 0.52)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.77) / wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.88 * tmp + 0.36)) / wp.abs((v0 + 0.78 + v2 + 0.75)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(0.15) / v1)
